To celebrate launch day, I'm giving away the complete Modern Essentials collection to five followers!!
To participate:
Follow @roseinc & @rosiehw
Like this image
Tag a friend using #roseincgiveaway in a comment
 
No purchase necessary to enter or win.
5 winners will receive one (1) Modern Essentials collection*
*Limit one shade of choice for any cosmetics in the collection
 
***Eligibility open to U.S. residents only and must be 18 or older to win. Void where prohibited by law. Ends on 8/29/2021 at 11:59pm ET. Winners will be selected at random, contacted from the @roseinc verified account only via DM by 8/31/2021 and receive their prize (ARV: $314) by September 30, 2021. Winners are responsible for taxes. Message and data rates apply. If winner does not respond to prize notification within 48 hours of message, a new winner will be selected. We do not send any registration links from other accounts. This promotion is in no way sponsored by, endorsed by, administered by, or associated with Instagram. By entering, entrants confirm they meet eligibility criteria, release Instagram and Clean Beauty Collective, Inc. of responsibility, and permit use of their name, image and likeness by Clean Beauty Collective, Inc.
